WEBVTT

00:12:25.149 --> 00:12:30.084
The handouts of free land
in places like Virginia

00:12:30.108 --> 00:12:31.798
to white people only

00:12:31.822 --> 00:12:35.810
started long before
the American Revolution

00:12:35.834 --> 00:12:37.699
and continued long after.

00:12:40.026 --> 00:12:42.294
Now, I can imagine

00:12:42.318 --> 00:12:46.666
there would be people listening to me --
if they're still listening --

00:12:46.690 --> 00:12:48.070
who might be thinking,

00:12:48.094 --> 00:12:52.456
"Come on, this is all ancient history.
Why does this matter?

00:12:52.480 --> 00:12:53.743
Things have changed.

00:12:53.767 --> 00:12:55.981
Can't we just get over it and move on?"

00:12:56.905 --> 00:12:58.056
Right?

00:12:58.421 --> 00:13:01.840
But I would argue, for me certainly,